_A modern redevelopment of the IslandsNow website using Next.js 2 to enhance performance and user experience._

[**View on GitHub**](https://github.com/jaydald/islandsnow-nextjs2.git)

---

### Overview

This project involved redeploying the IslandsNow website using Next.js 2 to take advantage of server-side rendering, improved routing, and enhanced performance. The goal was to modernize the site architecture and improve load times while maintaining the core content and branding.

---

### My Contributions

- Redeveloped the IslandsNow website using Next.js  
- Implemented concepts learned in class  
- Worked on routing, components, and layout improvements for a better user experience  

---

